        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/247/797/original/9cf7e974-1793-422a-afba-5cfd986af756.png" srcset="" alt="View Quizzes Page" height="222" width="606">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_24636B10-2228-0135-BD00-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>On the Quizzes Index Page, the quiz shows there are multiple users and dates assigned to the quiz. Hover over the text to view date availability.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
